{"id": 3093, "genre": 1000, "title": "为了社交减负，你希望社交 app 可以增添哪些新的功能？", "description": "想要缓解社交焦虑，来说说你都有哪些真实需求吧。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 5780, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191217213906PkmIyocCF7wKQj0u.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-17T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6119, "title": "为了社交减负，你希望社交 app 可以增添哪些新的功能？", "content": "为了给线上社交减负，你希望社交app可以增添哪些新的功能？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 350838, "content": "除了置顶，屏蔽消息也能设置沉底", "image": "img/option/option/20191217204004clBzoPSItUL0Fn6s.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350839, "content": "群聊可以屏蔽特定群成员的消息", "image": "img/option/option/20191217204301pAZvJMrj3HuGmo8t.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350840, "content": "关注时推荐相似内容，取关时也能提供“不感兴趣”列表", "image": "img/option/option/20191217204458SZPbQnr2OqEWMRFk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350841, "content": "热点时评关联相关新闻提示，否则不知道在讨论啥", "image": "img/option/option/20191217204627pwmaqU7vi1jdyFkl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350842, "content": "除了共同关注推荐，还能跟好友共享黑名单", "image": "img/option/option/20191217204758hs79jmWoGnxZ2DKz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350843, "content": "一键拉黑给某条评论点赞用户", "image": "img/option/option/20191217205106rS7duD2ALwOXpekE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350844, "content": "自动双向取关/（被）删除好友能从彼此的列表中消失", "image": "img/option/option/20191217205445Vdor3teCGz1bn0iP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350845, "content": "我还有其他想法", "image": "img/option/option/20191217205728e6IV47fimga5WwcH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}